title: Cami Li plans to tone down her sexy pics: 'It’s time to grow up and put some clothes on.'
text:
GETTY COVERING UP: Cami won't flaunt her hot bod as much 
In a lengthy Instagram post the beauty revealed that it’s now time for a change. 
She said: "I don't know what I'm doing, except that I'm transitioning this page into something different. 
"For years I've done modelling and as much as I LOVED it, it's time to grow up & put some damn clothes on." 
INSTAGRAM/CAMI_LI CHANGE: Cami has revealed she will stop posting her cheeky pics Cami Li smoulders in cut-out swimsuit Thursday, 6th October 2016 The gorgeous Cami Li smoulders in cut-out swimsuit as she poses with tattooed model 1 / 18 
The outspoken celebrity continued: "I’m 30 now (jeez, I can't even say that out loud) and it's time to start the next chapter in my life. 
"That being said, I've got my big girls panties on and will not be posting as many sexy photos anymore." 
The former Celebrity Big Brother housemate added: "I wanna thank everyone who supported me the past eight years and I am forever in your debt. 
INSTAGRAM/CAMI_LI TATTOOED: The beach babe hopes she will continue to be supported Cami Li Sexy Valentine's Day pics of the gorgeous Cami Li 1 / 7 Form Photos Happy Valentine's day from Cami Li “I hope you choose to stay and learn a different side of me, the cooler one. ” Cami Li 
"I hope you choose to stay and learn a different side of me, the cooler one. 
"Don't get it twisted, I will still post risqué photos, but nothing implied or nothing that'll make sure your shit needs to be on work-safe mode. 
"I definitely plan on interacting more with you guys and hopefully we can figure this journey out together. I love you all. Girl, bye!" Related videos
